%% Sequence: Pipeline inference
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant P as pipeline(task)
    participant T as Tokenizer
    participant M as Model
    participant B as Backend (Torch/TF/JAX)

    U->>P: call(inputs)
    P->>T: preprocess(inputs)
    T-->>P: tokenized tensors
    P->>M: forward(tensors)
    M->>B: compute on device(s)
    B-->>M: outputs (logits)
    M-->>P: outputs
    P->>T: postprocess / decode
    T-->>P: strings / structured outputs
    P-->>U: final predictions
